      "parameters": {
        "content": "### Required Fields Present?\n\nTwo-way gate on `={{ $json.query }}`. TRUE continues the happy path, FALSE takes the alternate branch.\n\nPorts: ①→ Classify with AI · ②→ Abort — Malformed Input",
